column5: Leaving for quinte in an hour I couldn't sleep for the last 4 hours Does this happen to all of us ?
not 4 hours early - but yeah, pretty much every time an hour before I have to. Good luck.
Yes...  Happens to me all the time...  Plan a huge day of fishing...12-18 hours with the drive... And only get 3-4 hours of sleep...  I'm like a kid on christmas...  Wife laughs every time...
Well the insomnia was worth it killed em on quinte today
